      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's an interesting distinction. When you say Profile B's background might be seen as \"contributing to the offense,\" do you mean the court would treat his socioeconomic status as an aggravating factor that justifies more time in jail rather than rehabilitation? Can you expand on why one is seen as a candidate for mercy and the other as a higher risk?",
